  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/8400c920f86d2aae52c09cad43a3d87c.poster.avif?t=1765381894\" width=744 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/8400c920f86d2aae52c09cad43a3d87c.webm?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/8400c920f86d2aae52c09cad43a3d87c.mp4?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hometown has grown quieter over the years. It's time to leave, and the only way out is up! But can you even make it to the end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bat and your wits are all you need to surpass any obstacle! Climb to the heavens, and discover the secrets across the valley in this <strong>challenging</strong> puzzle - execution - momentum game!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes. There are checkpoints. That way I can make it harder! ( and more satisfying )</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your progress is always saved baby</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand drawn sprites / characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep mechanics behind simple unorthodox controls (bat)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A movement system that has lots of depth and mastery! use that brain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles that seem impossible at first, but always have clean solutions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I believe in you!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No limits! go as fast as you can no one will catch you*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of secrets I put a lot of secrets I think good luck!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A handful of characters!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No combat*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >creacher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uhhh mini games?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(background) animals that rhyme with bat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(background) animals that dont rhyme with bat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*(you can go <strong>real</strong> fast)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/bb3e5c8f97c8576d7bbe30585e9f4ab6.poster.avif?t=1765381894\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/bb3e5c8f97c8576d7bbe30585e9f4ab6.webm?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/bb3e5c8f97c8576d7bbe30585e9f4ab6.mp4?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>use brain!! warning brain use may be required</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/8400c920f86d2aae52c09cad43a3d87c.poster.avif?t=1765381894\" width=744 height=386 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/8400c920f86d2aae52c09cad43a3d87c.webm?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/8400c920f86d2aae52c09cad43a3d87c.mp4?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your hometown has grown quieter over the years. It's time to leave, and the only way out is up! But can you even make it to the end?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bat and your wits are all you need to surpass any obstacle! Climb to the heavens, and discover the secrets across the valley in this <strong>challenging</strong> puzzle - execution - momentum game!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yes. There are checkpoints. That way I can make it harder! ( and more satisfying )</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your progress is always saved baby</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand drawn sprites / characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep mechanics behind simple unorthodox controls (bat)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A movement system that has lots of depth and mastery! use that brain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging puzzles that seem impossible at first, but always have clean solutions!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I believe in you!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No limits! go as fast as you can no one will catch you*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of secrets I put a lot of secrets I think good luck!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A handful of characters!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No combat*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >creacher</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uhhh mini games?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(background) animals that rhyme with bat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(background) animals that dont rhyme with bat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*(you can go <strong>real</strong> fast)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/bb3e5c8f97c8576d7bbe30585e9f4ab6.poster.avif?t=1765381894\" width=800 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/bb3e5c8f97c8576d7bbe30585e9f4ab6.webm?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044100/extras/bb3e5c8f97c8576d7bbe30585e9f4ab6.mp4?t=1765381894\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i>use brain!! warning brain use may be required</i></p>",
